text.tspan: The new Experteer mobile experience steps away from a mere job board. It's different from competitors by providing
tailored content that is valuable for your next career step. Instead of asking you to operate a search engine, we do it for
you by knowing your wishes and needs.
As the only UX designer in the team, I was responsible for the user experience design: start from competitor analysis
and defined key features with product manager; conduct brainstorm session, created user flow, wireframe;
communicated with skateholder and team members, conduct design review meeting; together with visual designer I
also worked on final visual design, created and maintained design styleguide. By the second half of the
development, I helped product manager to supervise and test the implementation to make sure the final product
can meet the requirements and deadline.
UX+UI Design | The new Experteer mobile experience
